    "custom_liquid_FYW4t7": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<h2><center>Our Story</h2></ceright><br><right><p>With our mascot being birthed from a dream at the foothills of Mt. Fuji on an outdoor expedition after stories about the ancient ninja clans of old Japan, we knew the sky was the limit with DTF transfers. \n\n</ceright><br><right><p>The team at Ninja Transfers has worked for over a decade in the custom apparel business, doing eCommerce, screen printing, embroidery, and DTG. When the pandemic hit in 2020, we decided it’d be the perfect time to test new technologies to provide the best possible quality and service to our customers. When we first got our hands on some DTF samples, we knew we could take it to a new level and displace DTG entirely. \n\n</ceright><br><right><p>After testing countless combinations of ink, film, and powder, heating temperatures, curing time, and pressing time, we found our winning formula — and that’s when Ninja Transfers was born. \n\n</ceright><br><right><p>While we started by printing our own transfers to decorate apparel for our customers, we realized we could use the transfers we’d mastered to help other decorators and businesses nationally leverage DTF to grow or start their own businesses. \n\n</ceright><br><right><p>DTF and UV-DTF are not just our business; our Ninja eats, sleeps, and nun-chucks DTF every day. We are crazed about speed, quality, and service with no minimums. As the ONLY transfer we specialize in, we are the true experts in DTF transfers.",
        "full_width": false,
        "remove_margin": false
      }
    },
