        "text_9DnQfA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Birthed from a dream at the foothills of Mt. Fuji after hearing tales of ancient ninja clans, Ninja Transfers leverages over a decade of experience in custom apparel. During the 2020 pandemic, we tested new technologies and discovered the potential of DTF transfers, eventually perfecting a formula through rigorous testing. Initially used for our own apparel, we now help decorators and businesses nationwide. Our mascot epitomizes our dedication to speed, quality, and service, with no minimums. As the only transfer we specialize in, we are true experts in DTF transfers.</p>",
